    "Id": "chassisdef_pebble_crab_PCRB-27",
    "Name": "Pebble Crab",
    "Details": "The Pebble Crab PCRB-27 is a 35-ton Cosara Weaponries light BattleMech introduced in 3065 as a spiritual successor to the original Crab CRB-27, replicating its firepower in a significantly lighter frame. Two arm-mounted ER Large Lasers provide the primary long-range punch, supported by a center-torso ER Medium Laser for mid-range engagements and a head-mounted Small Pulse Laser at close range. Fourteen Double Heat Sinks allow the full weapons suite to be fired together with reasonable regularity despite the all-energy loadout.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Long</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_pebblecrab"
  },
  "VariantName": "PCRB-27",
